# This includes regular nouns, multi-POS nouns, and names that are nominalized even when bare
# postpositions
#This excludes irregular U, and infinitivals
#This excludes adverbs/adjectives and participles that are nominalized when non-bare


OpenClassRegularNounDeclCanBeBareStem NSg0 RegNounCaseIDeclensionWithOptDef
